{"tid":1511951,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（公投）十一我有個大膽想法，不如直頭搞個臨時政府出黎？ (修訂版)","createTime":"2019-08-27T16:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T19:18:46.000Z","uid":54303,"like":173,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"340a3308921c4581eda275a366cb8b4e444a73c2","tid":1511951,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:42:56.000Z","msg":"上一個post:<br />\n<br />\n（公投）十一我有個大膽想法，不如直頭搞個臨時政府出黎？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dKJsjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dKJsjS</a><br />\n-------------------------------------------<br />\n「臨時政府」、「臨時立法會」等等既諗法都唔係今日先有, 但係每次有人提起, 都會有好多巴打問有冇軍火, 有冇認受性等等, 而且仲有人選同憲法等既技術性問題。不過我係上一個post睇到一篇長文, 正好就講比我地聽點樣做。真係好長, 唔想睇字海就睇下面summary啦。<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%96%E8%AD%A6%E6%9A%B4-%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A-%E5%BE%9E%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E5%88%B0%E8%B5%B7%E7%BE%A9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259A%25B4-%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%258D%2587%25E7%25B4%259A-%25E5%25BE%259E%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%25BE%25A9%2F&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxsVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=1722a340\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259A%25B4-%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%258D%2587%25E7%25B4%259A-%25E5%25BE%259E%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%25BE%25A9%2F&h=fd9eeb75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%96%E8%AD%A6%E6%9A%B4-%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A-%E5%BE%9E%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E5%88%B0%E8%B5%B7%E7%BE%A9/</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單講, <span style=\"color: red;\">臨時政府要斬件上市</span>。先由較簡單、爭議性低既機關開始, 再一步一步組織起有技術性問題既機關。我地可以先整個民間獨立調查團(好似已有, 不過進度唔知), 政府唔檢控黑警我地就整個<span style=\"color: red;\">民間法院</span>出黎, 按證據同程序審黑警, 當事人唔出席答辯就係佢理虧。之後再臨立會, 最後先係行政機關。咁做既好處係全香港都憎黑警, 用佢地做切入點成立平行機構, 阻力應該比較細。而且成立臨時政府之前會有足夠時間對外宣傳, 可以睇下外國有咩反應, 會唔會支持將來既臨時政府。<br />\n<br />\n所以, 我建議十月一共匪建政日, 香港人宣佈成立民間法院出黎, 專門調查同呢次運動相關既警暴同濫權。地點可以揀終審法院/或者其中一間大學校舍。<br />\n<br />\n細節大家繼續傾, 希望大家就住大方向去表態:<br />\n同意請正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔同意負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3ee315566fac48f531e933d8ae1d45a59527b9","tid":1511951,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:43:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"197b7f9d64d20b9f8d6812ee88c7ef76e8e63fb9","tid":1511951,"uid":55128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxsVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=88f13dbd\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxsVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=e1f16811\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxsVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=16f185d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"306fcc35870efd6ba8e79f8689dcaf26aabc4a0d","tid":1511951,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:44:01.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5b93c288492f9205cc557fe34258af3c661040b7","tid":1511951,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"repl